name: LEPTON LAMP LORD
description:
Just back from a visit with the Venusian Vase Vender, the Lepton Lamp Lord is at once a lamp and a lord. What more could you ask from an ultra collectible NFT? 

Use the tools to manually adjust parameters. Note the beautiful ZIM components conveniently tiled in a panel. These control the color and animation of the ZIM Pen.

Dr Abstract is the Founder of ZIM and inaugural member of the Gadget Minters. See https://zimjs.com/nft and https://zimjs.com/gadgetminters
